data.description: Ready for move in! Beautiful curb appeal on a fantastic oversized cul-de-sac lot! Enjoy swinging from the tree swing in the front yard, and your view of the cul-de-sac watching kids playing or enjoying the outdoors.  This is a great location, tucked away in a quiet neighborhood. This three bed, three bath home offers, two living spaces inside, a two story outdoor patio for relaxation, a spacious, multi-use game room, sitting area in primary bedroom, and shed. Close to shopping and dining.
